//Bone marrow edema


Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 04 - Bones of Knee MRI
When I select the radio button 'Finding'
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Bone marrow edema' from the Finding dropdown
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled

And mulitple selection localizer is enabled
And 'Subchondral' radio button is enabled
And 'Circumscribed' radio button is enabled
And 'Diffuse' radio button is enabled

And 'Soft tissue edema' checkbox is enabled
And 'Synovial thickening with edema' checkbox is enabled
And 'Subchondral fracture' checkbox is enabled

And 'Transient osteoporosis' checkbox is enabled

When I select all 9 parts on the localizer
Then all 9 parts are selected and turn red
